Description: 【Adaptive Active Noise Cancellation】After the noise reduction is turned on, the SoundPEATS Air4 wireless earphones will automatically adapt to your ear canal, dynamically detect changes in environmental noise and wearing status, and dynamically adjust and match the most suitable noise cancellation parameters in real time. With a single pair of headphones, you can simultaneously connect to two devices such as smartphones, tablets, smartwatches, without the need for reconnection.
